item.title: Starting over. (server help)
item.dc:creator: @bl1tz bl1tz
item.description:
@bl1tz wrote:

so you have phonescape.

go to tuts sectiona nd look for a tut list.

get heros, kalph, kbd, and make alot of tele’s and a few commands like ::ghostly.

add some shops, like a pure stall, def noob stall and weapons stall.

make a few pk areas.

go to client.java, press ctrl+h, change “phonescape” to your servername.

change “admin” to your admins name.

run hamatchi blah blah blah =p then tell me ham adress so i can test.
